    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You incorporate your two-handed reach weapon into a dizzying martial dance.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Weapon Focus (any two-handed reach weapon), Perform (dance) 4 ranks.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Each time you hit a creature with a twohanded reach weapon that you have Weapon Focus in, the creature is dazzled for 1 round.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you inflict the dazzled condition on an opponent using the Spear Dancer feat, you can spend up to 5 stamina points to increase the duration of the effect by 1 round per stamina point spent.",
